quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,23,"OOn [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun …óa…ď…ďiri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe …óen o wi'i: "mi heblanii-mo-ma!" o maaki: "Moolaare Alla! Jey…óo kam on mo∆ī∆īinii weerde am. Si ko woni, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen maletaake"."
  12,24,"GooŇč…óii [debbo] on himmanii oon. KaŇčko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [min gerdiri] fii yo min njiiltu mo e bone e paŇčkare. Pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ďe amen la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďeen."
  12,25,"∆Āe …ói…óo kala …ďe ngidondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya oon …ďaawo. ∆Āe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: "Ko hol…óum woni njo…ďdi on paalanaa…óo …ďeynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muus…óe?""
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: "Ko kaŇčko …óa…ď…ďiri kam hoore-am". Tawanoo…óo e yim…ďe [debbo] on ceeditii: "Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] oon gooŇč…ói, kaŇčko [gorko] on ko jeyaa…óo e fen…ďe …ďeen."
  12,27,"Si tawii noon dolokke makko oon ka …ďaawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kaŇčko [gorko] on ko o jeyaa…óo gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'noo dolokke oon ko …ďaawo seekori, o wi'i: "∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon …óen ko maw…óe!"."
  12,29,"Yuusufa, …óuurno gah e …óum. Aan [debbo on], imsinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa …óin; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woop…ďe …ďeen"."
  12,30,"Rew…ďe …ďen ka saare mbi'i: "Debbo laam…óo on …óa…ď…ďirii kurka makko o hoore-makko! GooŇč…óii yi…óde …ďurtirii mo. Minen dey mi…óen nji'a oo [debbo] e majjere …ďanngunde"."